Sri Lanka Beats Kenya in Cricket World Cup; Lasith Malinga Gets Hat-Trick

-- B y   P e t e r - J o s e p h   H e g a r t y
-- 
2011-03-01T14:42:49Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-01/sri-lanka-beats-kenya-in-cricket-world-cup-lasith-malinga-gets-hat-trick.html
  Sri Lanka  beat  Kenya  by nine wickets
in a Cricket World Cup Group A match in  Colombo  today.  Kenya made 142 all out as Lasith Malinga took a hat-trick in his
6-38. Upul Tharanga scored 67 not out and Tillakaratne Dilshan
44 as Sri Lanka reached 146-1.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Peter-Joseph Hegarty at 
 phegarty@bloomberg.net  